{
  "texts": [
    "This robustness may be attributed to the inherent properties of the underlying generative model, Stable Diffusion [25], which we employ in our framework.",
    "A.10 More Generated Metamorphic VideosDue to space constraints, to demonstrate the robustness and generality of our approach, we present several textguided metamorphic video generation results in Fig. 27 and Fig.",
    "We also present additional metamorphic videos generated by MagicTime and other baseline methods in Fig. 29.",
    "It is clear that MagicTime consistently surpasses existing state-of-the-art Time-to-Video (T2V) models across various scenarios, from melting ice to the expansion of bread.",
    "These results showcase a robust understanding of physical phenomena encoded within the model."
  ]
}